{"tid":2188873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《財新》指長實擬出售北京、上海兩項物業　總值達 500 億人民幣","createTime":"2020-09-04T13:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T07:19:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8cea0524f082596f9e6291c59f21ef3f70a5215c","tid":2188873,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"內地媒體《財新》報道，長實集團（01113）計劃出售位於北京、上海兩項物業，總值達 500 億人民幣，中國地產發展商融創中國（01918）有意接手。<br />\n<br />\n《財新》報道中提到，計劃出售的物業分別是北京市朝陽區逸翠園二期項目，和上海普陀區高尚領域綜合體項目，屬商住兩用，目前交易仍在商議中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/傳長實出售北京-上海兩項物業-總值達-500-億人民幣/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%82%B3%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%A9%E9%A0%85%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E7%B8%BD%E5%80%BC%E9%81%94-500-%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=83eb6a5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%E5%82%B3%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%85%A9%E9%A0%85%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E7%B8%BD%E5%80%BC%E9%81%94-500-%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3%2F&h=9b279213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/傳長實出售北京-上海兩項物業-總值達-500-億人民幣/</a>"},{"pid":"d060193eb0ef957e022e1bbe93ef46cd8c11d915","tid":2188873,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"跑路"},{"pid":"47be8772ea3167eeaebeb5a72c6319c4c024b074","tid":2188873,"uid":374259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5956f307cdc6e7e17a3c629c3b8d5aecfe29c4d6","tid":2188873,"uid":254383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"咁失策仲未甩晒手上"},{"pid":"2b196d34133a5cc50c8a546ddc9082d948684cec","tid":2188873,"uid":155225,"like":0,"dislike":2